title: 191 - Top Gut
description:
Today’s podcast is a bit of a continuation from last week as the guys discuss the power and process of building a habit. Last week CJ mentioned one of ETA’s staff members and her weight loss journey. Today she joins the guys on the podcast and talks about the internal work that goes with building a habit that’s required to achieve a BIG goal. ET gives practical advice on how to attack a large goal without burning yourself out in the process.

  [07:25]  - Cheeto Puff Alert
